tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE NutrientCyclingData (
  EcosystemID INT PRIMARY KEY,
  NutrientName VARCHAR(50),
  SourceOrganism VARCHAR(50),
  SinkOrganism VARCHAR(50),
  NutrientCycleStage VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Nutrient_Exchange_Log (
    Log_ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    Date DATETIME,
    Sender_Location VARCHAR(50),
    Receiver_Location VARCHAR(50),
    Nutrient_Type VARCHAR(50),
    Nutrient_Amount FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE NutrientCyclingData (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location_name VARCHAR(50),
  nutrient_type VARCHAR(50),
  nutrient_level FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE EcosystemModels (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name VARCHAR(50),
  model_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE EcosystemDynamics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  time_period VARCHAR(50),
  ecosystem_changes TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ResearcherInfo (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  researcher_name VARCHAR(50),
  research_area VARCHAR(50),
  research_focus TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ecosystem_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    nutrient_type VARCHAR(255),
    nutrient_level INT
)

CREATE TABLE species_info (
    species_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    species_name VARCHAR(255),
    species_type VARCHAR(255),
    habitat VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE nutrient_sources (
    source_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    source_name VARCHAR(255),
    type VARCHAR(255),
    availability VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE species_interaction (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    species1_id INT,
    species2_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE nutrient_cycling (
    cycle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    source_id INT,
    destination_id INT,
    cycle_type VARCHAR(255)
)
